metadata.name: RINORI
metadata.description:
Rinori, a psycho gothic girl  
Dark thoughts consume her world  
She seeks revenge, a dark desire  
Her heart filled with flames of fire

She stalks her prey, a silent creep  
Her victim unaware, asleep  
But Rinori will have her way  
As she plots and plans each day

Her gothic style, all black and gloom  
Masks the pain that lies within her womb  
But soon her revenge will be at hand  
As she makes her victim's life withstand

Rinori, a psycho gothic soul  
Her revenge will be her ultimate goal  
But in the end, what will it bring  
Happiness or a never-ending sting?
